                     <interp inst="t18240715-159-person1399" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I saw the prisoner going towards the street door with a great coat on his arm - I asked him what he was going to do with it, he said to give it to a man in the street - I took it from him, and then pursued him to Fort's Livery stables, we met my master on returning.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 68.</p>
